\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 There were two invalid sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 When mother employed this person to do domestic work, where did she eat?
