rs in and churning, well father liked to have the company sometimes, he'd like me to go out you know with him. And - he'd talk away over things, but - he would take me to a market sometimes to see how things was going on or something like that you know, t
o see the things sold and - things like that. But - then - you always looked to mother for things, you know, I think -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 You could go to mother and talk to her easily?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Did she show affection very much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Yes. I think more so than
 father, father was - not affectionate, you couldn't call it affection, most - used to think he was a bit serious, a bit }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11809502\charrsid11542501 stern}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 
 at times, he get - you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 If you had any worries could you share them with your mother or not?
