\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Was it in a practical way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Well - you - you - not so much practical way, he look - you look back on things and you said, well - father used to thin}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11809502\charrsid11542501 k}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501  quite a bit, he used to do intelligent things that
 - we didn't think was very much in it those days but we do appreciate it now 'cos I remember him saying - that when you've gone - to - I've seen him do a deal with a job - with a man for - cattle or something like that and they would shake hands, they wo
u
ldn't give any written - receipt or anything like that, he'd shake hands on it and that would be it. That was their - that - that was - his bond. His hand was his bond. And - if he'd - thought that you've been in any trouble, I remember got in trouble wit
h
 the police once for taking pens out the wrong pen but that - that was all right, that was all settled up all right, but he said - told me to be very careful he said because an honest penny were bright. He used to tell me the old things, but - then someti
mes -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 An honest penny wears bright?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 
Yes. Well a simple thing that - sometimes you think he's a bit stern or a bit - think - when you think honest mistake but - he would like to have things straight - you know, and as I told you before he wouldn't
 stand any lies or any - any funny business you see. If you asked him in the right manner, if you wanted a bike or wanted something he would try and get it for you. Some reason - within reason you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 What was the story you told me about when you had new smart clothes, what was his remark about that?
