Well mother happened to look up to me and said - I had a new plus fours and - I felt - was going to ride this motor bike and - she said to dad - didn't you think that suit looked nice on Wilfred, sh
e said, well it does - he didn't say it did or no, he said, well - my opinion, he said, that - poor - it's very poor ground and wants so much top dressing. So -
\par 
