\insrsid11809502\charrsid11542501 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 unds, he - he came home and - when I was there the manager gave me a shilling, which I thought was a lot of money, which was a lot of money in those days, 
and when I came home he said - he was talking to mother and he said, well the rent's paid again dear. But he said, I don't know where next shilling is coming from.
