Well I don't know, we was never encouraged to be fighting yet my - my father was a bit of a wrestling man, he - and that, but he - he's never an aggressive man, I've never seen him in a brawl nor - or - he was never drunk nor - smoke, 
and he - I never seen him in a brawl nor in a - blows with anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 No fighting for fighting's sake?
