nd used to get special service at St Buryan feast - go down there to the farm and go up to the - chapel, there used to be a special service like but nothing - used to get a bazaar there sometimes I think or a cricket match but we didn't - very seldom didn
't have long enough for that, it didn't used to stop so long down there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 When you went to stay a night or two with relatives, which members of the family went besides yourself?
