Yes, generally, one of others would go occasionally, the elder ones. If I was driving a car and mother and dad wanted to go I'd take them down to the Feast and they would - spend the - dinner there and perhaps teatime 
and others at home would carry on a little bit of work was on, and then I'd bring them back again, there would be just the day's journey, like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 That's since you've grown up?
