\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 You didn't go to chapel regularly?
