\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 This was at St Just?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 'Cos we was a mile and a half, perhaps two miles sometime from the chapel and we - that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Did you have different special clothes to wear on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Well yes, yes, we generally kept best clothes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Were you allowed to play games on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Well not much, not really, no, we didn't have to - we never played any cards or any - cricket or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Did your parents think it wrong to work or play on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Well they - th
ey - there was never - we would never do unnecessary work, we would never go out with - with a - on the ground and working horses and stuff and that sort of thing like some do - my father used to keep the Sunday sacred, the cows had to be milked and thing
s tended to as far as that go that's finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Just the necessary work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Just the Necessary.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 For the farm?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Did your parents attend a place of worship or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Well - not - regularly. Not as a family grew up it was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Always the farm to be seen to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 
Yes, they used to have more - when they was younger they used to go to chapel and church, mother played the organ - when she was younger but - they used to like to go and - when they went to feasts they liked to go to 
the service sometimes at the Sennen church or Sennen chapel or somewhere like that they used to like to go if they went down there you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Special days, that would be like harvest festival?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Yes. Yes, and all that, that's right, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Anniversary?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Yes, that's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 What denomination chapel would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4475040 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Wesley - was, yes yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 Sennen Wesley?
