Well - well - more or less when I said my father used to take us down to the - front room of a Sunday morning when we was catched up with work and he - we'd have a bit - he'd tell - one of us to read a bit of the Bible allowed, was to learn
 to read the Bible and - explained it to us and - had a bit of - he'd have a bit of prayer sometimes or a bit of - sing a hymn.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6778144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1389977\charrsid11542501 That would be of a Sunday morning?
